  <CalDefinition Description=":  GDMPRS-999 - The map matching and position refinement function shall exhibit a calibration parameter Ke_FreewayMode. If Ke_FreewayMode=True, the map matching shall assume that the vehicle stays always on roads of class 1 and 2 or the direct connections (exit/entrance ramps) of those roads.  GDMPRS-999a" Name="AHP_MPP_RestrictionToFreewayMode" References="GIS-628 Appendix B" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
