  <CalDefinition Description="Minimal sub-path length, see Appendix B. Note: The value range for this calibration is 100-800 meters, and the default value is 100 meters as defined in the GIS-628 Specification." Name="AHP_Content_MinSubPathLength" References="GIS-628 Appendix B" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
